<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@600;700&display=optional');

  :root {
    --bg: #14251a;
    --surface: #1f3627;
    --ink: #edf5ee;
    --muted: #b7ccb9;
    --line: #365341;
    --brand: #f19c42;
    --brand-strong: #de7d1f;
    --accent: #89c795;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.56;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 0, #22412e 0, var(--bg) 40%), var(--bg);
  }

  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

  .page { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.25rem 4rem; }

  .topbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.05rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .brand { font-weight: 800; color: var(--brand); letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .path { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; }

  .hero { padding: 3rem 0 2.2rem; }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.11em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.45rem);
    line-height: 1.06;
  }

  .lead { margin: 1rem 0 1.35rem; max-width: 62ch; color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.02rem; }

  .primary-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--brand);
    color: #1f2f22;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 0.62rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.16rem;
  }

  .primary-cta:hover { background: #ffb86b; }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 0.9rem;
    margin: 1.6rem 0 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .hero-img-credit { display: block; text-align: right; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 0.3rem 0 0; }

  .proof {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.8rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .proof-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.92rem;
  }

  .proof-card strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .proof-card span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.86rem; }

  .section-title { margin: 0 0 0.9rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; }

  .apps-grid { display: grid; gap: 0.9rem; }

  .app-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 0.9rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .app-head { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.58rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .app-index { color: var(--brand); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
  .app-title { margin: 0; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800; }
  .app-tagline { margin: 0 0 0.45rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .app-desc { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.92rem; }

  .actions { margin-top: 0.82rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .open-btn {
    border: 1px solid var(--brand);
    border-radius: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffe2c5;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .open-btn:hover { background: rgba(241, 156, 66, 0.12); }

  .minor-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.65rem; }
  .minor-actions a { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.8rem; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }

  .closing {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    background: #f19c42;
    color: #243625;
    border-radius: 0.95rem;
    padding: 1.32rem;
  }

  .closing h2 { margin: 0 0 0.45rem; font-size: 1.22rem; }
  .closing p { margin: 0 0 0.9rem; }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .proof { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<div class="page">
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">Vibes DIY</a>
    <span class="path">/summer-camp/</span>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Camp staff operations</p>
    <h1>Keep daily camp logistics moving without spreadsheet drag.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Five practical staff apps for arrivals, duty rotation, activity signups, lost-and-found, and pickup tracking during peak camp days.</p>
    <a class="primary-cta" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/camp-arrival-board" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Cabin Arrival Tracker</a>
    <img class="hero-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472745433479-4556f22e32c2?w=1200&q=80&auto=format" alt="Group of campers gathered around a campfire at dusk" loading="eager">
    <a class="hero-img-credit" href="https://unsplash.com/@mischievous_penguins" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Photo by Mike Erskine / Unsplash</a>
  </section>

  <section class="proof" aria-label="Summer camp value strip">
    <article class="proof-card"><strong>Built for rush hours</strong><span>Clear screens for check-in, transitions, and pickup windows.</span></article>
    <article class="proof-card"><strong>Staff-friendly</strong><span>Low training overhead for seasonal teams and volunteers.</span></article>
    <article class="proof-card"><strong>Adjustable fast</strong><span>Clone and tune each app for your own camp workflow.</span></article>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Open the operational app you need now</h2>
    <div class="apps-grid">
      {{#each apps}}
      <article class="app-card">
        <div class="app-head">
          <span class="app-index">APP {{num}}</span>
          <h3 class="app-title">{{title}}</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="app-tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="app-desc">{{desc}}</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="open-btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open app</a>
          <div class="minor-actions">
            <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clone</a>
            <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Remix</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="closing">
    <h2>Start with arrivals, then layer other workflows.</h2>
    <p>Open Cabin Arrival Tracker first to stabilize check-in, then add duty, activity, and pickup tools as camp day pressure rises.</p>
    <a class="primary-cta" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/camp-arrival-board" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Cabin Arrival Tracker</a>
  </section>
</div>
